doc.after: This page explains and provides the guidelines for the review process associated with the pending changes protection feature enabled on 1 December 2012 Articles with pending changes applied can be reviewed by administrators or users called pending changes reviewers who hold the pending changes reviewer permission The process of reviewing is intended as a quick check to ensure edits don t contain vandalism violations of the policy on living people copyright violations or other obviously inappropriate content
